query:
UPDATE notebook_headers 
				SET hash = $1, 
					changed_accounts_root = $2, 
					changed_account_origins = $3, 
					chain_transfers = $4, 
					tax=$5, 
					block_voting_power=$6,
					block_votes_root=$7, 
					block_votes_count=$8, 
					finalized_block_number=$9,
					blocks_with_votes=$10,
					secret_hash=$11,
					parent_secret=$12
				WHERE notebook_number = $13
